T2 Trainspotting is a 2017 British comedy drama film , set in and around Edinburgh , Scotland .
The film is directed by Danny Boyle and written by John Hodge , based on characters created by Irvine Welsh in his novel Trainspotting and its follow-up Porno .
T2 was released in the United Kingdom on 27 January 2017 and worldwide throughout February and March 2017 .
A sequel to Boyle 's 1996 film , Trainspotting , T2 stars the original ensemble cast , including Ewan McGregor , Ewen Bremner , Jonny Lee Miller , Robert Carlyle , and Kelly Macdonald .
T2 is deliberately self-referential , with film-clips , music and echoes from the first film .
The screenplay is based on Porno , with characters and elements lifted from the novel Trainspotting .